metadata.name: Confidence
metadata.description:
Confidence,

Knowing your worth, believe in your own abilities, embrace your strengths, and seize the opportunity.

Being perfect or knowing all the answers is not the key of confidence. 
You have the power to conquer the world and make your dreams come true. Be unique and celebrating who you are.

Remember that confidence is a part of your journey, is built on self love and self acceptance. Radiate The Confidence and inspire others.

-Confidence is a part of your journey-
-自信はあなたの旅の一部です-
-自信是你旅程的一部分-

Character
Name: Dai Mei Xuan 戴美旋
